    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no chips, scratches, or dents. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and garage-kept its entire life. This is a rare find for a discerning collector or buyer who demands the absolute best in quality and presentation.",
