    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to even write this, but it\u2019s time for this absolute gem to find a new home. If you\u2019re like me and appreciate a car that\u2019s been treated with nothing but love, you\u2019re going to adore this one. It\u2019s in truly pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014I\u2019ve personally made sure it stayed tucked away from the elements and kept it looking sharp enough to turn heads at every stoplight. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth and responsive, just like the day it was born. I\u2019ve poured my heart into keeping this beauty perfect, and I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will do the same. Come on over, let's grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself how special she is!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
